snippet.title: For Conservatives Only
snippet.description:
If you are a conservative, you have just found your new favorite YouTube channel! We post daily clips of Conservative/Republican public figures and political topics of interest. Some will get you thinking, while others will make you laugh uncontrollably. Make sure to subscribe so you don't miss a thing.

We also run an online store with the trendiest Conservative designs. We ship WORLDWIDE. Click the link to check out our collection.
